title: 2000AD 1861 (2013) (Digital) (Nahga-Empire) (- Nem -)
description:
Everything ends this prog as the current line-up of stories come to an end before next weeks Annual Prog 2014. Just four stories this prog, with a double-helping of 'Flesh'.

Cover: Henry Flint (Flesh)

    Judge Dredd - Ferals (part 4 - final part) (Emma Beeby - John Burns)
    Flesh - Badlanders (part 12 - final part) (Pat Mills - James McKay and Lee Townsend)
    Brass Sun - The Diamond Age (part 12 - final part) (Ian Edginton - INJ Culbard)
    Damnation Station - After Losing Every Battle (Al Ewing - Mark Harrison)
